        <div n="Y20-760L">
          <head type="note" n="1" xml:id="spp-Y20-760L-headnote-1">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-Y20-760L-headnote-1-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-Y20-760L-headnote-1-line-group-1-line-1">by D<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> <hi rend="large-writing">Arbuthnot</hi>.</l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="2" xml:id="spp-Y20-760L-headnote-2">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-Y20-760L-headnote-2-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-Y20-760L-headnote-2-line-group-1-line-1">Respicite Exemplar Vitæ────</l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-Y20-760L-headnote-3">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-Y20-760L-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-Y20-760L-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-Y20-760L-line-1" n="1">“How vain are Mortal Man's Endeavours!</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y20-760L-line-2" n="2">“Said at S<hi rend="superscript">ṭ</hi> <hi rend="large-writing">James's</hi>, Master <hi rend="large-writing">Travers</hi>.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y20-760L-line-3" n="3">“Good <hi rend="large-writing">Orleans Dead</hi>!── In truth, 'tis hard!</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y20-760L-line-4" n="4">“May <hi rend="large-writing">Statesmen</hi> all, dye so prepar'd!</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y20-760L-line-5" n="5">“I do foresee (and for foreseeing</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y20-760L-line-6" n="6">He equalls any Man in being)</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y20-760L-line-7" n="7">“The Army ne'er can be disbanded──</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y20-760L-line-8" n="8">“I wish the King were safely Landed:──</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y20-760L-line-9" n="9">“Ah friends! Great Changes threat this Land;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y20-760L-line-10" n="10">“All <hi rend="large-writing">France</hi> and <hi rend="large-writing">England</hi> at a Stand!</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y20-760L-line-11" n="11">“There's <hi rend="large-writing">Miriweys</hi> d'ye mark! strange Work!</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y20-760L-line-12" n="12">“And there's the <hi rend="large-writing">Czar</hi>; and there's the <hi rend="large-writing">Turk</hi>!</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y20-760L-line-13" n="13">“The <hi rend="large-writing">Pope</hi>”──── An<hi rend="large-writing"> India Merchant</hi> by</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y20-760L-line-14" n="14">Cut short his Speech with this Reply.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y20-760L-line-15" n="15">“<hi rend="large-writing">All at a Stand! You see; Great Changes</hi>!</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y20-760L-line-16" n="16">“Sir, did you ever see the <hi rend="large-writing">Ganges</hi>?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y20-760L-line-17" n="17">“There dwells a Race, we call 'em <hi rend="large-writing">Monkeys</hi></l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y20-760L-line-18" n="18">(Grave, Sober, Sage, as our <hi rend="large-writing">Quid nuncis</hi>.)</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y20-760L-line-19" n="19">“On either Bank, from bough to bough,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y20-760L-line-20" n="20">“They meet, and Chat as we do now:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y20-760L-line-21" n="21">“Whispers go round, they grin, they Shrug,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y20-760L-line-22" n="22">“They bow, they Snarle, they Scratch, they hug;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y20-760L-line-23" n="23">“And just as <hi rend="large-writing">Chance</hi> or <hi rend="large-writing">Whim</hi> provoke 'em,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y20-760L-line-24" n="24">“They either Bite their friends, or stroke 'em.</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y20-760L-line-25" n="25">“There have I seen some Active Prig,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y20-760L-line-26" n="26">“To shew his Parts, bestride a twig;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y20-760L-line-27" n="27">“<hi rend="large-writing">Lord</hi>! how the chatt'ring tribe admire</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y20-760L-line-28" n="28">“Not that he's Wiser, but is Higher!</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y20-760L-line-29" n="29">“All long to try the <hi rend="large-writing">Vent'rous thing</hi>,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y20-760L-line-30" n="30">(For <hi rend="large-writing">Power</hi> is but to have one's <hi rend="large-writing">Swing</hi>)</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y20-760L-line-31" n="31">“From Side to Side he springs, he Spurns,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y20-760L-line-32" n="32">“And bangs his Foes and Friends by turns.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y20-760L-line-33" n="33">“Thus, as in giddy freaks he bounces,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y20-760L-line-34" n="34">“Crack goes the twig, and in he flounces;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y20-760L-line-35" n="35">“Down the Swift Stream the Wretch is born</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y20-760L-line-36" n="36">“Never, ah! never to return.</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y20-760L-line-37" n="37">“<hi rend="large-writing">Zounds</hi>! what a Fall has our Dear <hi rend="large-writing">Brother</hi>!</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y20-760L-line-38" n="38">“<hi rend="large-writing">Morbleu</hi>, cries one, and <hi rend="large-writing">Dam──e</hi> 'tother:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y20-760L-line-39" n="39">“The <hi rend="large-writing">Nations</hi> give a <hi rend="large-writing">Gen'ral Sc</hi>\<hi rend="italics">ins</hi>·h\<hi rend="large-writing">riech</hi>.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y20-760L-line-40" n="40">“None cocks his Tail, none claws his br──ch;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y20-760L-line-41" n="41">“Each trembles for the Publick Weal,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y20-760L-line-42" n="42">“And for a while forgets to Steal:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y20-760L-line-43" n="43">“A while, all Eyes intent and Steady,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y20-760L-line-44" n="44">“Pursue Him whirling down the Eddy;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y20-760L-line-45" n="45">“But, out of mind when out of View,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y20-760L-line-46" n="46">“Some other mounts the twig a new,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y20-760L-line-47" n="47">“And Bus'ness on Each <hi rend="large-writing">Monkey</hi> Shore</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y20-760L-line-48" n="48">“Runs the same track it went before.</l>
          </lg>
